                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 511.4A1/1480.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Delegate <persName type="from">Van Dyke</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The Hague</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-06-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 20, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Germany and Portugal decline to put the Convention into effect until Turkey,
                    Greece and Serbia come in; Great Britain will wait for Germany. Yesterday’s
                    meeting adjourned till Monday. May we agree to put the Convention into effect
                    with a limited number of Powers?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Van Dyke</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
